erlands)|CU]]\n| 10 November 2015 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2015|11|10}})</small>\n| 20 September 2012 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2012|09|20}})</small>\n|-\n| style=\"background:{{Party for the Animals/meta/color}};\"|\n| [[File:Esther Ouwehand (cropped).jpg|120px|Esther Ouwehand]]\n| [[Esther Ouwehand]] <br/> <small>(born 1976)</small>\n| [[Party for the Animals|PvdD]]\n| 9 October 2019 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2019|10|09}})</small> <br/> <br/> 9 October 2018 \u2013 <br/> 31 January 2019 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2018|10|09|2019|01|31}})</small> <br/> <br/> 24 January 2012 \u2013 <br/> 14 May 2012 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2012|01|24|2012|05|14}})</small>\n| 18 October 2016 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2016|10|18}})</small> <br/> <br/> 30 November 2006 \u2013 <br/> 17 November 2015 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2006|11|30|2015|11|17}})</small>\n|-\n| style=\"background:{{50PLUS/meta/color}};\"|\n| [[File:Henk Krol 2013.jpg|120px|Henk Krol]]\n| [[Henk Krol]] <br/> <small>(born 1950)</small>\n| [[50PLUS|50+]]\n| 10 September 2014 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2014|09|10}})</small> <br/> <br/> 20 September 2012 \u2013 <br/> 4 October 2013 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2012|09|20|2013|10|06}})</small>\n| 10 September 2014 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2014|09|10}})</small> <br/> <br/> 20 September 2012 \u2013 <br/> 4 October 2013 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2012|09|20|2013|10|06}})</small>\n|-\n| style=\"background:{{Reformed Political Party/meta/color}};\"|\n| [[File:KeesvanderStaaijDirkHol2016.jpg|120px|Kees van der Staaij]]\n| [[Kees van der Staaij]] <br/> <small>(born 1968)</small>\n| [[Reformed Political Party|SGP]]\n| 9 June 2010 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2010|06|09}})</small>\n| 19 May 1998 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|1998|05|19}})</small>\n|-\n| style=\"background:{{Denk (Dutch political party)/meta/color}};\"|\n| [[File:FaridAzarkan2017.jpg|120px|Farid Azarkan]]\n| [[Farid Azarkan]] <br/> <small>(born 1971)</small>\n| [[Denk (political party)|DENK]]\n| 22 March 2020 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2020|03|22}})</small> <br/> <br/> 23 April 2018 \u2013 <br/> 2 September 2018 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2018|04|23|2018|09|02}})</small>\n| 23 March 2017 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2017|03|23}})</small>\n|-\n| style=\"background:{{Forum for Democracy (Netherlands)/meta/color}};\"|\n| [[File:Thierry Baudet (2018).jpg|120px|Thierry Baudet]]\n| <small>[[Doctor (title)|Dr.]]</small> <br/> [[Thierry Baudet]] <br/> <small>(born 1983)</small>\n| [[Forum for Democracy|FvD]]\n| 23 March 2017 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2017|03|23}})</small>\n| 23 March 2017 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2017|03|23}})</small>\n|-\n|colspan=\"10\" style=\"background: #C0C0C0\"|\n|-\n!colspan=3|[[Independent politician|Independent]] <br/> [[Parliamentary leader]]\n!Group/Member Name <br/> Former Party <br/> Seat(s)\n!Service as Parliamentary leader\n!Service as a Member of <br/> the House of Representatives\n|-\n| style=\"background:{{Independent/meta/color}};\"|\n| [[File:Profielfoto Femke Merel Arissen.jpg|120px|Femke Merel van Kooten]]\n| [[Femke Merel van Kooten|Femke Merel <br/> van Kooten]] <br/> <small>(born 1983)</small>\n| Member Van Kooten <br/> <small>(Left the [[Party for the Animals|PvdD]])</small> <br/> 1\n| 16 July 2019 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2019|07|16}})</small>\n| 4 February 2019 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2019|02|04}})</small> <br/> <br/> 23 March 2017 \u2013 <br/> 15 October 2018 <br/> <small>({{Age in years and days|2017|03|23|2018|10|15}})</small>\n|-\n| style=\"background:{{Independent/meta/color}};\"|\n| [[File:Netherlands politic personality icon.svg|120px]]\n| [[Wybren van Haga]] <br/> <small>(born 1967)</small>\n| Member Van Haga <br/> <small>(Expelled from [[People's Party for Freedom and Democracy|VVD]])</small> <br/> 1\n| 24